Description: Linux Task Manager - System monitoring tool
 A GTK+ system monitoring application that combines the functionality
 of Linux's top command with the user interface style of Windows Task Manager.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time CPU and memory usage graphs
  - Process management with user/system process separation
  - Logged-in users monitoring
  - System information display
 .
 This tool provides a familiar task manager interface for Linux users,
 designed to work on Linux Mint 22.1 and compatible distributions.